                        <br/><br/><br/><h2>文 献</h2><br><ol><br><li id="R1"><span class='au'>Fuster, J. M.</span>: <span class="ti">The Prefrontal Cortex, 4th Ed.</span> <span class='so'>Academic Press, San Diego (2008)</span></li><br><li id="R2"><span class='au'>Bauer, R. H. & Fuster, J. M.</span>: <span class="ti">Delayed-matching and delayed-response deficit from cooling dorsolateral prefrontal cortex in monkeys.</span> <span class='so'>J. Comp. Physiol. Psychol., 90, 293-302 (1976)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/819472" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R3"><span class='au'>Funahashi, S., Bruce, C. J. & Goldman-Rakic, P. S.</span>: <span class="ti">Dorsolateral prefrontal lesions and oculomotor delayed-response performance: evidence for mnemonic "scotomas".</span> <span class='so'>J. Neurosci., 13, 1479-1497 (1993)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/8463830" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R4"><span class='au'>Kopec, C. D., Erlich, J. C., Brunton, B. W. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">Cortical and subcortical contributions to short-term memory for orienting movements.</span> <span class='so'>Neuron, 88, 367-377 (2015)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/26439529" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R5"><span class='au'>Fuster, J. M. & Alexander, G. E.</span>: <span class="ti">Neuron activity related to short-term memory.</span> <span class='so'>Science, 173, 652-654 (1971)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/4998337" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R6"><span class='au'>Li, N., Chen, T. W., Guo, Z. V. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">A motor cortex circuit for motor planning and movement.</span> <span class='so'>Nature, 519, 51-56 (2015)[<a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25731172" target="_blank">PubMed</a>]</span></li><br><li id="R7"><span class='au'>Lee, S., Kruglikov, I., Huang, Z. J. et al.</span>: <span class="ti">A disinhibitory circuit mediat